  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the creepy village of Breinroth, inspired by popular memes. There are unique escape routes and deadly dangers waiting for you in the village. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Retro Graphics</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >minimalistic interface</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >gloomy atmosphere</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >deep diving</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play with your friends!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team up with a friend to explore the village. Be careful: The bomber crocodile is watching from above so that you don't escape.</p>",
